On Wed, 5 Nov 2003, Rob Carpenter wrote:

> someone elses measurement would be, running 14" tires.
> i need the measurement from top of tire to bottom of
> fender well..


Problem is that with different tire sizes this measurement might vary by
an inch one way or another.

A better way is to put the vehicle on a level surface, put a 200 pounder
in the front seat, and check the deck inside the sliding door with a
level.  If it's close to level you're good!

George
